com.gmail.yuyang226.flickr.places
Class Location

java.lang.Object
  com.gmail.yuyang226.flickr.places.Location

public class Location
extends Object

A Flickr place.
As a result to PlacesInterface.getInfo(String, String) a Location describes the relation of a place to various types of other places.
